README

How to install the demo?

- Install kurento media server.
    sudo apt-get install kurento-media-server
- Install the facesegmentator module for the media server and restart the server.
	sudo apt-get install kms-face-segmentator
	sudo service kurento-media-server restart

- Add kurento bower repository:
  · Create ~/.bowerrc file.
  · Add:
  
  { 
   "registry": "http://bower.kurento.org:5678" ,
   "strict-ssl": false
  }

- Update the bower dependencies. 
    bower install (from the root directory of the tutorial)

-Install an http server:
	sudo npm install http-server -g

- Run the http-server:
	http-server

- And now the demo is available in the indicated url by http-server.
